(17982, 0, 50, 7, 12, 'Demolierer Legoso', 'There''s no turning back now, $N. Stay close and watch my back.', 'There it is! Do you see where the large red crystal is jutting out from the Vector Coil? That''s where I need to plant the first set of explosives.', 'Cover me!', 'It won''t be much longer, $N. Just keep them off me while I work.', 'That''ll do it! Quickly, take cover!'),
